node.text: Now more than ever, it’s our turn to #PlayItForward to the frontline workers who continue to keep our communities safe and healthy. For each eligible @Barbie Paramedic, Doctor, or Nurse doll sold at @Target through August 28, @Mattel will donate $5 to the @1stRCF, up to $50,000, supporting the families of our bravest heroes. Play, inspire, and give back – what’s better than that? #ThankYouHeroes
